data.description: This charming property boasts an elegant façade adorned with pristine white stone complemented by a sleek metal roof, creating a striking visual appeal. Inside, you'll find a spacious living area with tasteful tile flooring that adds a touch of sophistication to the space. The centerpiece of the living room is a beautifully crafted floor to ceiling rock fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings and a glass front china cabinet. The home features a thoughtfully designed mother-in-law plan, providing both privacy and convenience. The Primary bathroom has a unique sliding mirror to allow natural light and the ability to be mirrored over double vanity. Kitchen includes a unique drop down cook/recipe book holder directly under the cabinet. Numerous & recent upgrades, including freshly interior and exterior paint, new water heater & repairs. Step outside to discover a delightful screen porch (23X12), where you can enjoy the outdoors while being protected from the elements. Additionally, this property offers a spacious and cedar lined closet within the utility room and ample storage space, making organization a breeze. Property includes an attached 12X11 workshop and a detached greenhouse. You'll also appreciate the close proximity to a convenient boat launch at Jones Brothers Park. Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your own – it combines practicality, comfort, and natural beauty to create a truly remarkable living experience.
